==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Couching
<hw>Couch"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>The
operation of putting down or displacing the opaque lens in
cataract.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Embroidering by laying the materials upon the
surface of the foundation, instead of drawing them through.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Couchless</ent>⟦br⟧
